/ColdTurkey   <-- Root-level Main application (writes to hosts file)
/CT_notify    <-- User-level background process to trigger CT_popup and block programs
/CT_notify2   <-- User-level background process to monitor CT_notify
/CT_popup     <-- User-level program that is the popup displayed when the time is up
/kctrp_srv    <-- Root-level Windows service (lock hosts file) and unblocks user when time is up
/SetACL       <-- Root-level program that is used for a Windows Defender (Win 8) work around (freeware)

Created and compiled with Visual Studio VB.NET 2010

